{"tid":494781,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"比個挑戰比將會喺聖誕假晚晚通頂打機同睇劇嘅巴絲","createTime":"2017-12-10T04:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T05:12:52.000Z","uid":152376,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0488972b8eedf632abfca5c574770225b3662dcc","tid":494781,"uid":152376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"通頂打機完 第日起身基本上見唔到陽光 之後仲要極度嘅攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">比個挑戰大家 有無種假期每晚12點前訓 8點起身再打</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n計計埋埋可能仲多咗時間打<br />\n可以唔洗爆肝<br />\n又可以見到美好嘅陽光<br />\n又可以落街買個早餐食<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">諗起都充滿力量</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有種挑戰嘅留低你嘅正皮</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每日充滿精神咁去打機同睇劇 身體又健康過人 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇種挑戰嘅咪負皮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  慢慢爆爛你個<span style=\"color: red;\">垃圾肝</span>"},{"pid":"b903b717aa3beb923e2a0a8e392fca7824fd5a9f","tid":494781,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:11:13.000Z","msg":"又係依啲投正負評post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">正左評</span>"},{"pid":"5c64d63576a15831699111b3e4767dbd51348ae1","tid":494781,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:25:13.000Z","msg":"有冇因爲返工要通頂嘅巴絲<br />\n我宜家諗下都想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor